=== Erdrick's Equipment ===
All Erdrick's equipment is present:
* Erdrick's Sword - Charlock Castle
* Erdrick's Armor - Hauksness ruins
* Token - Swamp south of Cantlin

=== Rainbow Bridge ===
Create the bridge to Charlock:
* Collect Sun Stone
* Collect Rain Staff
* Use at Rainbow Shrine

=== Hidden Treasure ===
Several treasures are hidden:
* Search all chests thoroughly
* Some require keys
