== Dragon Quest II Secrets ==

=== Crest Locations ===
All five crests are needed:
* Sun Crest - Sea Cave
* Moon Crest - Tower of the Moon
* Star Crest - Fire Shrine
* Water Crest - Water Temple
* Life Crest - Dragon's Horn

=== Charm of Rubiss ===
Essential for defeating Hargon:
* Found in Rubiss Tower
* Requires solving the tower puzzle
* Breaks Hargon's barrier

=== Princess Rescue ===
Moonbrooke princess is cursed:
* Find Mirror of Ra
* Use in Moonbrooke Castle
* She joins your party

